### Sentences and transformation {.text-center}

**Q25.** “We were no more surprised than Rahman” — meaning?
Answer: We were as surprised as Rahman

**Q26.** “Not once has our neighbour invited us into his house” — meaning?
Answer: Our neighbour has never invited us into his house

**Q27.** Travellers — their reservation well in advance.
Answer: had better get

**Q28.** After food has been dried or canned — for later consumption.
Answer: it should be stored

